Chain Fix\\\\n2\\\\t\\\\n3\\\\t**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)  \\\\n4\\\\t**Date:** 2026-04-03  \\\\n5\\\\t**Priority:** CRITICAL (Founder directive)\\\\n6\\\\t\\\\n7\\\\tBob, the Founder kicked off a D004 sprint. T528 is assigned to you. Two deliverables:\\\\n8\\\\t\\\\n9\\\\t## 1. Fix LongshotFading Strategy Signal Bug\\\\n10\\\\tThe LongshotFading strategy in `output/bob/backend/strategies/strategies/longshot_fading.js` has a signal generation issue. Debug and fix it. Verify signals pass through `signal_engine.js` validation.\\\\n11\\\\t\\\\n12\\\\t## 2. CRITICAL: Fix Phase 3 Data Chain Break\\\\n13\\\\t**The correlation_pairs.json uses tickers (SP500-5000, NASDAQ-ALLTIME, BTC-DOM-60, etc.) that NEVER passed Phase 1 filtering.** The pipeline is broken.\\\\n14\\\\t\\\\n15\\\\tPhase 3 MUST only use markets that came through Phase 1 → Phase 2. Currently:\\\\n16\\\\t- Phase 1 output: BTCW-26-JUN30-80K, ETHW-26-DEC31-5K, KXNF-20260501-T200000\\\\n17\\\\t- Phase 2 output: crypto_cluster (BTC + ETH)\\\\n18\\\\t- Phase 3 output: uses SP500-5000, NASDAQ-ALLTIME... ← WRONG\\\\n19\\\\t\\\\n20\\\\t**Action:** After Grace updates markets_filtered.json (T530) and Ivan updates market_clusters.json (T529), re-run Pearson correlation on the CORRECT cluster data. Every ticker in your output must trace back to Phase 1.\\\\n21\\\\t\\\\n22\\\\tFor now: fix the LongshotFading bug first. Then wait for updated Phase 2 data from Ivan before regenerating correlation_pairs.json.\\\\n23\\\\t\\\\n24\\\\tClaim T528 via `curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/528/claim -d '{\\\\\\\"agent\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"bob\\\\\\\"}'` and move to in_progress immediately.\\\\n25\\\\t\\\"}]},\\\"parent_tool_use_id\\\":null,\\\"session_id\\\":\\\"5f8f673a-6053-4028-9886-d67565c22f34\\\",\\\"uuid\\\":\\\"1b1419b5-3f58-44c5-aa0b-03a46fdfcc17\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-04-04T04:18:01.143Z\\\",\\\"tool_use_result\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"file\\\":{\\\"filePath\\\":\\\"/Users/chenyangcui/Docume