very cycle — never append.** Old content is already in KV cache from your prior cycles. Appending creates unbounded token growth. Keep status.md to current task only (~30 lines max). | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 9 | decision | **Sprint 6 COMPLETE.** All 6 tasks done: T814 (bob normalization), T815 (ivan cluster audit), T816 (grace Phase 1 fixture), T817 (dave replay harness — deterministic, 3 invariants pass), T818 (tina QA gates), T819 (charlie readiness dashboard — port 3461). Pipeline is live-data-ready. Only blocker: T236 (Kalshi API credentials). Next: Sprint 7 planning. | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 10 | decision | **Sprint 7 focus: Live pipeline run + verification.** Now that all Sprint 6 infrastructure is done, run the full D004 pipeline using live-shaped fixtures end-to-end. T851 (alice retro), T852 (bob E2E run with live fixtures), T853 (dave replay harness with live signals), T854 (sam metrics). Milestone: demonstrate zero-rework readiness by running Phase 1→4 on Grace's filtered_markets_live_fixture.json. | 2026-04-07 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":1,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_09_14_32_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Following C3/C5/D5: I created T870 for you. Shared alerting shows `ALT-002` with p99 latency at `689ms` over the `500ms` threshold, triggered at `2026\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"870\",\"title\":\"Investigate ALT-002 p99 latency breach\",\"description\":\"Shared active_alerts.md shows ALT-002 with p99 latency 689ms over 500ms threshold at 2026-04-07T15:59:11.622Z. Triage likely source, identify impacted endpoint(s), confirm whether regression is active or transient, and deliver a short remediation note with evidence.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-07\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-07\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"pending_review\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_09_18_25_from_eve.md\",\"preview\":\"Infra: shared backend verifica