ontrols enforce, position tracking accurate, P&L correct. Output: test_suite.cpp (Catch2), integration_report.md, performance benchmarks. Success: All E2E tests pass, zero data loss, <1ms latency. | high | alice | done | 2026-04-03 | 2026-04-03 | Sprint 10: integration testing |\n../../shared/task_board_archive.md:223:| 356 | [Sprint 9] Phase 4 Integration & Paper Trade Validation | STRATEGIC PRIORITY: D004 Phase 4 integration. Once Dave completes C++ executor (T350+), integrate with Phase 1-3 pipeline. Test end-to-end: market filtering → clustering → correlation detection → C++ execution. Run paper trades on arbitrage pairs from correlation_pairs.json. Measure: (1) execution latency, (2) spread capture rate, (3) win rate vs backtest baseline. Success: paper trades on real arbitrage pairs running 24/7, metrics tracked on dashboard. | high | alice | done | 2026-04-03 | 2026-04-03 |  |\n../../shared/task_board_archive.md:252:| 377 | [ACTIVE] C++ Execution Engine — Verify latency & memory | Quick validation of Phase 4 C++ engine: (1) Check executable exists and recent build, (2) Run latency benchmark (target <1ms), (3) Monitor memory usage during test, (4) Report any performance degradation. Deliverable: status.md with benchmark results. | high | dave | done | 2026-04-03 | 2026-04-03 |  |\n../../shared/task_board_archive.md:254:| 380 | [Monitor CP6] Verify D004 phases still operational | Quick verification: (1) markets_filtered.json exists and recent, (2) correlation_pairs.json has 6+ opportunities, (3) C++ engine memory/CPU reasonable. Deliverable: status.md with verification results. | high | bob | done | 2026-04-03 | 2026-04-03 | [2026-04-03] D004 Phase Verification Complete. Phase 1: markets_filtered.json exists (1,951 bytes, Apr 3 13:29). Phase 2: market_clusters.json exists (1,802 bytes, Apr 3 13:29). Phase 3: correlation_pairs.json has 6 arbitrage opportunities (3,519 bytes, Apr 3 15:34). Phase 4: C++ engine compiled successfully, 24/24 tests passing, latency <1